16:55.041 --> 16:56.489
See a client.

16:57.134 --> 16:59.168
Told her it was a bad idea, but...

16:59.620 --> 17:01.122
[SCOFFS]
she wouldn't listen.

17:01.382 --> 17:04.505
Well, Grovetown's always a bad idea.

17:05.353 --> 17:07.281
I mean, she can take care of herself.

17:07.819 --> 17:09.032
She's smart.

17:09.257 --> 17:11.279
Maybe too smart for her own good.

17:12.351 --> 17:14.005
She called me from there yesterday.

17:14.693 --> 17:16.449
I didn't like the way she sounded.

17:16.930 --> 17:19.228
Well, I tried.
I tried everything.

17:19.867 --> 17:21.469
Told her, "Baby, come on home,"

17:21.502 --> 17:25.111
but she just said,
<i>"I can't. Not yet."</i>

17:25.938 --> 17:28.703
Thing that's got me shook,
though, is...

17:29.085 --> 17:30.369
h-how she said it.

17:32.109 --> 17:33.328
Sounded scared.

17:34.409 --> 17:36.244
Where do I come into all this?

17:36.270 --> 17:38.093
I want you to go down there
and bring her home.

17:38.119 --> 17:39.418
- What, me?
- You.

17:40.086 --> 17:41.421
What... What about you?

17:41.455 --> 17:42.986
I'm back with the wife.

17:43.012 --> 17:45.348
It wouldn't look good I go
chasin' after Florida, you know?

17:45.526 --> 17:47.712
- Well...
- 'Sides, I got kids.

17:47.805 --> 17:49.173
It's Christmas.

17:49.363 --> 17:51.174
But you, you got nobody.

17:51.794 --> 17:54.219
- I got Leonard.
- Well, his ass is in jail.

17:54.334 --> 17:56.036
Shit, Hanson.

17:57.104 --> 17:58.576
Grovetown?

17:58.840 --> 18:00.899
- Send Charlie.
- Charlie's police.

18:01.575 --> 18:04.204
This ain't police business.
It's personal.

18:08.394 --> 18:09.947
You do this for me,

18:11.202 --> 18:13.837
I'll let Leonard out of jail
when you get back.

18:17.509 --> 18:19.111
I do this for you,

18:20.348 --> 18:22.783
you gotta let Leonard
out of jail now.

18:23.998 --> 18:25.267
Tonight.

18:28.936 --> 18:31.539
<i>["I'M GONNA LASSO SANTA CLAUS"</I> PLAYS]</i>

18:31.572 --> 18:34.976
♪♪

18:35.008 --> 18:37.578
Grovetown gives shitholes
a bad name, Hap.

18:37.612 --> 18:40.634
Yep.
I've heard the stories.

18:40.925 --> 18:43.364
It's a two-hour ride
but a hundred years away.

18:43.918 --> 18:45.253
They don't like black folk there

18:45.286 --> 18:48.055
unless they swabbin' out the
toilet or sweepin' the floor

18:48.088 --> 18:50.501
or steppin' off the curb
let the white man pass.

18:50.958 --> 18:52.905
Klan's alive and kickin' there.

18:53.160 --> 18:56.230
Call themselves the Supreme
Order of Caucasian Assholes,

18:56.264 --> 18:57.486
some such shit.

18:57.763 --> 19:00.308
Well, if it's so bad, why did
Hanson ask us to go there?

19:00.334 --> 19:02.237
Well, he ain't askin' you.
He's askin' Hap.

19:02.269 --> 19:04.305
- Well, it's the same thing.
- No, it ain't the same thing!

19:04.337 --> 19:07.075
Guy like you in Grovetown start
the next goddamn Civil War.

19:07.107 --> 19:08.976
Well, I can't help it
if I'm burstin' with charm.

19:09.009 --> 19:11.808
You're burstin' with bullshit's
what you're burstin' with.

19:12.680 --> 19:14.315
Now, Hap, you take my advice.

19:14.347 --> 19:16.483
You go down there,
you get in, you get out.

19:16.517 --> 19:18.327
You don't take Leonard with you.

19:19.054 --> 19:21.128
Grovetown and black folk don't mix,

19:21.154 --> 19:23.579
and Leonard Pine does not
play well with others.

19:24.935 --> 19:27.004
[CAR DOOR CLOSES]
CHARLIE: Remember what I said!

19:27.193 --> 19:29.360
Be back in an hour, partner.

19:29.926 --> 19:31.667
We'll take my car.

19:32.065 --> 19:34.201
Should hit Grovetown by morning.

19:34.235 --> 19:36.371
I'll get the sandwiches and the guns.

19:36.513 --> 19:38.484
What do we need guns for?

19:39.054 --> 19:40.288
Never know.

19:40.408 --> 19:42.443
Might be in the mood
to shoot somethin'.

19:42.476 --> 19:44.112
[SIGHS]

19:44.399 --> 19:46.243
You don't need to do this, ya know.

19:46.797 --> 19:48.423
Ain't doin' it for you, Hap.

19:48.449 --> 19:50.078
Florida's family.

19:51.106 --> 19:52.993
Yeah. Right.

19:53.020 --> 19:54.155
Oh, hey.

19:54.407 --> 19:55.487
Nearly forgot.

19:56.055 --> 19:57.464
Merry Christmas.

19:59.125 --> 20:00.527
You shouldn't have.

20:01.318 --> 20:02.735
Man, I ain't get you nothin'.

20:03.021 --> 20:04.151
I know.

20:05.364 --> 20:07.467
You're the only gift I need, Leonard.

20:08.721 --> 20:10.523
[ENGINE STARTS]

