21:29.784 --> 21:31.786
[DOG BARKS IN DISTANCE]

21:31.818 --> 21:33.754
[CREAKING]

21:47.941 --> 21:50.360
Aaaaah!

21:51.285 --> 21:52.987
[GRUNTING]

21:54.993 --> 21:56.328
- Come on, man!
- Come on, please!

21:56.360 --> 21:57.528
We don't want...
We don't want no trouble!

21:57.561 --> 21:59.231
The hell you doin' in my house?

21:59.263 --> 22:01.098
Was guardin' the house next
door, but then we got hungry,

22:01.131 --> 22:02.767
and them crackheads
don't got shit to eat.

22:02.800 --> 22:05.070
- Ah...
- Yeah! Yeah, we went to get pizza,

22:05.102 --> 22:07.772
came back, and we seen you
burnt the place down again.

22:07.806 --> 22:08.807
Yeah, and the cops took you in,

22:08.840 --> 22:10.876
so we just figured
we'd use your place to eat.

22:10.908 --> 22:12.631
This look like a cafeteria to you?

22:12.657 --> 22:15.312
No. But it's a real nice place
you got.

22:15.346 --> 22:17.382
There's some pizza in
the kitchen if you're hungry.

22:17.415 --> 22:18.983
- You can have some.
- Yeah.

22:19.016 --> 22:20.084
Yeah, you can have it.

22:21.675 --> 22:23.311
What kind of pizza?

